  "text": [
    "when you drop",
    "your mate at",
    "the dock or",
    "your children",
    "at school. Don\u2019t",
    "be cool. Don\u2019t",
    "be coy. Or if",
    "you do, don\u2019t",
    "assume it\u2019s",
    "okay to act",
    "that way. For",
    "today may",
    "be your last",
    "chance at",
    "joy before it",
    "flashes away",
    "like a tin",
    "toy in one of",
    "those shooting",
    "galleries in",
    "midways: those",
    "ducks that seem",
    "to paddle a",
    "stream that\u2019s",
    "not a stream",
    "but a rotating",
    "axle,",
    "toothed for",
    "disappearance",
    "& reappearance,",
    "a spit",
    "without point",
    "or flame,",
    "along which",
    "randomly clucks",
    "the whole game."
  ],
  "title": "Don\u2019t Be Flip",
  "year": ""
}